OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773245482
OL,3,CSon's manslaughter plea after stabbing
OL,4,Cand strangling mum
OL,6,FA trial of facts was held in 2024,
OL,7,Fwhen a jury found Parker had carried
OL,8,Fout the killing. He was given a
OL,9,Fhospital order.
OL,11,FIn July of last year he was reassessed
OL,12,Fas being fit to stand trial for murder
OL,13,Fbut following medical assessments, he
OL,14,Fwas found to have diminished
OL,15,Fresponsibility and a manslaughter plea
OL,16,Fhas now been accepted.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
