OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773245482
OL,3,CSon's manslaughter plea after stabbing
OL,4,Cand strangling mum
OL,6,FDet Supt Nicola Burnett, of Humberside
OL,7,FPolice, said: "This was a tragic and
OL,8,Fsenseless killing that has left a
OL,9,Ffamily utterly heartbroken by the loss
OL,10,Fof their loved one in truly horrific
OL,11,Fcircumstances.
OL,13,F"They have been through a harrowing
OL,14,Ftribulation, and my thoughts remain
OL,15,Fwith them at this incredibly difficult
OL,16,Ftime."
OL,18,FHull Crown Court previously heard
OL,19,FParker had developed mental health
OL,20,Fproblems following a road accident.
OL,26,@oD@OOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
