PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773245482
OL,3,CSon's manslaughter plea after stabbing
OL,4,Cand strangling mum
OL,6,FHe attacked her on 5 March 2023 after
OL,7,Fshe called for an ambulance to get him
OL,8,Ftreatment.
OL,10,FParker himself called 999, telling the
OL,11,Fcall handler: "There is a woman who
OL,12,Fhas been badly injured."
OL,14,FPolice and paramedics found his mother
OL,15,Fin the hallway with a stab wound to
OL,16,Fher chest.
OL,18,FAs well as murder, Parker was charged
OL,19,Fwith assault after headbutting and
OL,20,Fpunched his step-father in a previous
OL,21,Fattack.
OL,26,@sD@OOU
